  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879850/extras/4e3ef8819a245e41df8b2a4ac921f608.poster.avif?t=1633383672\" width=600 height=44 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879850/extras/4e3ef8819a245e41df8b2a4ac921f608.webm?t=1633383672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879850/extras/4e3ef8819a245e41df8b2a4ac921f608.mp4?t=1633383672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>You play as a cube and every cube you touch attaches to you and every cube those cubes touch attach to them.<br><br>The goal is to make the shape on the ground with the colours in the correct spot.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879850/extras/2b507f7aedff37e3a5e019c80c06b289.poster.avif?t=1633383672\" width=600 height=44 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879850/extras/2b507f7aedff37e3a5e019c80c06b289.webm?t=1633383672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879850/extras/2b507f7aedff37e3a5e019c80c06b289.mp4?t=1633383672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>Compete with people from all around the world to try and get the least amount of moves using the leaderboard.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879850/extras/b34cdd42ec4adbf0e176dabc3e505ef4.poster.avif?t=1633383672\" width=600 height=44 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879850/extras/b34cdd42ec4adbf0e176dabc3e505ef4.webm?t=1633383672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879850/extras/b34cdd42ec4adbf0e176dabc3e505ef4.mp4?t=1633383672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>50 Levels<br></li><li>Colour blind mode<br></li><li>Colourful levels<br></li><li>Cool shapes<br></li><li>Challenging puzzles<br></li><li>Leaderboards</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879850/extras/4e3ef8819a245e41df8b2a4ac921f608.poster.avif?t=1633383672\" width=600 height=44 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879850/extras/4e3ef8819a245e41df8b2a4ac921f608.webm?t=1633383672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879850/extras/4e3ef8819a245e41df8b2a4ac921f608.mp4?t=1633383672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>You play as a cube and every cube you touch attaches to you and every cube those cubes touch attach to them.<br><br>The goal is to make the shape on the ground with the colours in the correct spot.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879850/extras/2b507f7aedff37e3a5e019c80c06b289.poster.avif?t=1633383672\" width=600 height=44 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879850/extras/2b507f7aedff37e3a5e019c80c06b289.webm?t=1633383672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879850/extras/2b507f7aedff37e3a5e019c80c06b289.mp4?t=1633383672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>Compete with people from all around the world to try and get the least amount of moves using the leaderboard.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879850/extras/b34cdd42ec4adbf0e176dabc3e505ef4.poster.avif?t=1633383672\" width=600 height=44 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879850/extras/b34cdd42ec4adbf0e1